<h5 id="subject_686767">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=d02c2b8ebfdf44378e526f6c0f474323&amp;topic=72895.msg686767#msg686767" rel="nofollow">【暗影狂奔第五版核心规则书翻译】创建人物 p.62 --  </a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_686767'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_686767'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong> 于:</strong> 2014-12-14, 周日 18:17:45 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_686767_quick_mod"></div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_686767">创建一名暗影狂奔者<br><br>跟我读，开始：<br><br>当心背后！<br>瞄准再打！<br>节约弹药！<br>决不和龙打交道！<br><br>在暗影狂奔的世界生存需要遵守一些基本法则。除此之外，每个人都有他们自己的一套，或者根本没有。有人从劫富济贫，也有人劫富笑贫；有人明目张胆地做着犯罪的勾当，也有些人神龙见首不见尾，除非他想，否则没人能见到他。<br><br>重点是，暗影狂奔者形形色色，而现在该你创建自己的角色，并踏上 2075 年的街道。全力出击，挑战不可知的命运，祈祷你能成功，并且让所有人都看到你有让不可能变可能的胆量和手段。你或许永不会被“文明”社会接纳，但你可以为此而骄傲——你的一切都是自己挣来的，包括自由。<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Those are the fundamental rules for surviving in the <br>Shadowrun world. Beyond that, individuals have their <br>own rules—codes, or lack thereof. There are peo-<br>ple who steal from the rich and give to the poor, and <br>people who steal from the rich and laugh at the poor. <br>People who are flamboyant, pulling off capers in grand <br>style, and people who are never seen, not for a second, <br>by those they don’t want to see them.<br>The point is, there are all types of shadowrunners out <br>there, and it is time now to create one and take to the <br>streets of 2075. Take your best shot, fight the odds, hope <br>for the best, and show everyone you have the guts and <br>the skills to do the impossible. You may never be accept-<br>ed in “civilized” society, but you can take pride in the <br>fact that you’ve earned everything you own—including <br>your freedom.</div></div></div><br>第一步：选择角色概念<br><br>边栏：常见角色概念与定位解释为你列出了阴影世界中最常见的人物类型。联合各自的专长，技能，和专业领域来完成他们单枪匹马时难以完成的任务。所以特工们会为了某个特定的任务而暂时合作，也可能在整个职业生涯中都保持搭档关系，亲密如同家人。这一节只是抛砖引玉，暗影世界中有很多人物无法被划入任何一类。你创建的角色是独一无二的。<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">The sidebar&nbsp; Common Character Concepts and their <br>Roles Explained gives you a snapshot of the character <br>types your most likely to find in the shadows. Dispa-<br>rate characters band together as runner teams; blend-<br>ing their talents, skills, and specialized expertise to <br>complete missions they would not be able to pull off <br>as individuals. Some runner teams come together for a <br>specific job, while others stay together throughout their <br>entire careers, becoming as close-knit as family. This <br>gallery is just a starting point—there are characters in <br>the shadows that don’t conform to any list. The one you <br>create will be uniquely yours.</div></div></div><br>角色创建小提示<br><br>大意就是你可以用excel，word，或者纸笔来做卡，别忘了算临时加减值之类的。没啥意义就跳过了。<br><br>你可以先大致想好你要做个什么样的角色，以及一些基本的背景。角色可能曾经是某个国家的士兵，现在将自己的战斗技巧用来混街道。或者是个前公司猎头，因为在激烈的竞争中被巨头公司排挤，现在靠自己的谈判与交易技巧在暗影中求生。也有些二代暗影狂奔者，生于此道并从他们没有身份识别码的父母那里学到了各种技能。赏金猎人为了超自然生物的毛皮或者追猎逃犯而在暗影行动中掺一脚也是很常见的事情。角色可能是在街道帮派中长大，将暗影行动视为摆脱身边那些人渣的方法。又或者她刚刚离开监狱，想看看凭自己的能力和在里面的关系能否有所作为。<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">You may start with an idea of what sort of charac-<br>ter you want to play and some basic background con-<br>cepts. The character may be an ex-soldier from a na-<br>tional government looking to use her combat skills on <br>the streets. Or a former corporate headhunter forced <br>out of the megacorporation by an ambitious rival and <br>now using his negotiating savvy and deal-making skills <br>to survive the shadows. There are second-generation <br>runners, born to the life and learning the skills of the <br>trade from their SINless parents. It’s not unusual for a <br>bounty hunter who collects pelts of paranormal critters <br>or tracks down fugitives to engage in a little shadow-<br>running to supplement his income. The character may <br>have grown up in a street gang, and he sees shadow-<br>running as a way to get out of the gutter. Or the char-<br>acter may have just gotten out of jail and be eager to <br>see what she can do with the skills she learned and the <br>connections she made on the inside. </div></div></div><br>你刚开始不需要了解角色概念和角色数据的细节。那些可以慢慢来。现在只需要脑子里有一个概念，然后不断挖掘它。你的角色很快就会变得与众不同，而且完全属于你。<br><br>pc 和 gm 应该互相合作，创建一个适合模组的小队。这里的规则适用于创建一名有经验的暗影狂奔者。想要创建其它类型的角色（街头小子，精英特工）请参见可选游戏边栏。<br><br>暗影狂奔的所有角色起始拥有25业力点来提升自己。你会随着游戏进行得到更多业力点。<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">You do not need to understand all the nuances of <br>character creation and character statistics to get started. That will come with time. To start, have a concept <br>in mind and dive in. Your character will quickly become<br>unique—and all yours.<br>Players and the gamemaster should work together <br>to develop a team of characters that are suited to the <br>campaign. The character creation rules as presented <br>in this chapter involve the creation of an experienced <br>shadowrunner. For rules on the other levels of characte<br>creation (street level, prime runner), see the Alternate <br>Gameplay Sidebar.<br>All characters in Shadowrun start with 25 Karma <br>they will use to improve themselves. They’ll get plenty<br>of other resources as they move through the process.</div></div></div><br>常见角色概念与其定位<br><br>出面人：出面人操控着他人的需求，如同音乐大师弹奏琴弦。他是骗术大师，闪闪发亮的谈判家，通常也是优秀的领导者。在谈判桌上和约翰逊先生（Mr. Johnson 是个行话，指交付任务的人）讨价还价是他的专长，尤其是交易伴随着巨大利益的时候。出面人也擅长搜集信息，哄骗诱导，或是从目标那里榨取确保自己任务完成的关键情报。虽然出面人通常都能靠社交与微笑达到目标，但他们也会变得更有威胁性以迫使目标说出秘密。语言是出面人选择的武器，魅力和意志是出面人的两项关键属性——但假如状况需要，他也可以毫无困难地抄起一把阿瑞斯掠夺者。<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Face: The face runs his fingers over the thrumming <br>strings of other people’s wants and needs, <br>playing them like a maestro. He is master of <br>the con, a polished negotiator, and often an <br>expert leader. Interacting with Mr. Johnson <br>during the meet is his specialty, especially when <br>it comes to bargaining for the greatest profit. The <br>face also excels at legwork, coaxing or squeezing <br>vital information from a variety of sources that could help make sure <br>his job is a success. Though the face usually manages to get what he <br>wants with charm and a smile, he knows how to be more forceful to <br>get people to cough up their secrets. Words are the face’s weapon <br>of choice and Charisma and Willpower are the face’s two important <br>attributes—but he has no problem using an Ares Predator when the <br>situation warrants. </div></div></div><br>施法者：胸前来一发魔法矢，迎面一个火球——这就是施法者的战斗方式。而他能做的还不止这些。他能操纵和引导名为法力的能量场，而那正是魔法的本质。不同的施法者操纵法力的方式也不同。魔法师遵循的是个比较注重逻辑与秩序的魔法体系，而萨满则更多依靠本能和直觉。要成为一名施法者，角色需要选取一项能赋予他魔法属性等级的优点（见优点表格，p.65）。视流派不同，施法者的重要属性可能是魅力或者直觉，意志也是抵抗耗竭的重要属性。<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Spellcaster: A manabolt to your chest, a fireball in <br>your face—that’s what the spellcaster brings <br>to the table in combat. And he does so much <br>more. He manipulates and channels mana, <br>an energy field that is the essence of magic. <br>Mana can be manipulated in several different <br>ways, allowing for different types of spellcasters. <br>Magicians follow a more logical and ordered system of magic, <br>while shamans rely more on their instincts and intuition. To make a <br>spellcaster, a player needs to select a priority that grants a Magic <br>attribute rating (see Priority Table, p. 65). Depending on the tradition, <br>Charisma or Intuition can be important attributes for spellcasters, and <br>Willpower is an important attribute for resisting Drain. </div></div></div><br>谍客：她是矩阵中的魔术师，是虚拟视野里稍纵即逝的闪电——谍客擅长于黑掉任何一台电脑，通讯链，甚至数据港口。她的工作通常涉及潜入，伪装，操纵和伪造数据，或者篡改安保系统使得她的小队能轻易出入防卫森严的部门。优秀的谍客很清楚她的工作通常会让自己置于白热化的战场的最中心，而她也知道该如何应对自如。无论是自己开枪，瘫痪掉敌人的武器，还是把战场上所有的电子设备派去战斗，谍客有很多方法让自己参与到战斗中。与谍客形影不离的是她的数据板（p.227），也是她完成一切活计的工具。逻辑，直觉，和意志是谍客的重要属性。<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Decker:&nbsp; The trickster in the Matrix, the flash of <br>lightning in the corner of your virtual eye—a <br>decker specializes in hacking into computers, <br>commlinks, and datahavens. Her job often <br>involves stealing, altering, and manipulating <br>data as well as taking control of or modifying <br>security systems so her teammates can get in and <br>out of defended facilities. A good decker knows her work may put <br>her right in the middle of heated action, and she knows how to react. <br>Whether she’s firing a weapon, disabling the weapons of others, or <br>sending every electronic device in a place on the attack, she has a whole bunch of options to keep herself involved in unfolding combat. <br>A decker never travels without her cyberdeck (p. 227), the tool of her <br>trade. Logic, Intuition, and Willpower can be important attributes for <br>the decker character. </div></div></div><br>技术巫师：有些人用物理手段入侵矩阵，而还有少数人能仅凭自己的意志登录矩阵。这些人就是技术巫师。技术巫师可以凭借自身的意志，通过某种内在链接访问矩阵。这种链接的原理直到今天仍不明确——尽管有无数人愿意花大笔经费来把它搞清楚。想扮演技术巫师的玩家需要在优点列表（p.65）里选择一项能给予你共鸣属性的。逻辑、直觉和意志是技术巫师的重要属性。<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Technomancer:&nbsp; Some people hack the Matrix <br>with physical tools, but a few have the ability <br>to log on with nothing more than their <br>minds. These people are technomancers. <br>A technomancer can access the Matrix <br>with his mind through an intrinsic connection <br>that’s not fully understood, even in 2075—<br>though plenty of people would pay plenty to figure out how it works. <br>A player who wishes to play a technomancer must select an option <br>on the Priority Table (p. 65) that gives the character a Resonance <br>attribute. Logic, Intuition, and Willpower can be important attributes <br>for the technomancer. </div></div></div><br>机械师：有些人只是驾驶车辆，而有些人将载具作为自己身体的延伸，如同一套额外肢体。机械师是专业的驾驶员，以及各类机械的王牌操纵着。她能熟练操作，维修，改装各类载具和/或无人机，给小队提供警戒，运输，以及远程火力。机械师最关键的属性是反射。<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Rigger:&nbsp; Some people drive cars; other people <br>use vehicles as an extension of their body, <br>like an additional set of limbs. A rigger is a <br>professional driver, an ace controller of all <br>sorts of machines. She is highly skilled in the <br>operation, repair, and customization of all sorts <br>of vehicles and/or drones, offering surveillance, <br>transportation, and remote firepower to their team. Reaction is a <br>critical attribute for riggers. </div></div></div><br>街头武士：有些艺术家用水彩作画，有些用油彩。街头武士是痛苦方面的艺术家。在任何环境下，他都知道至少十五种伤害敌人的方法，以及额外八种能把敌人伤害得惨绝人寰的方法。他能承受大量伤害而屹立不倒，并将毁灭性的伤害原数奉还给敌人。典型的街头武士往往装备着大量机械设备或者生化设备，以使得他无论武装还是徒手战斗都极其坚韧与致命。尽管街头武士既残忍又危险，他往往也会遵守某种原则——可能是某种只有他自己才理解的原则，但仍然不容忽视。体质、力量和敏捷是街头武士玩家最重要的属性。<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Street Samurai: Some artists work in watercolors, <br>some in oils. The street samurai is an artist <br>of pain. In any given situation, he knows <br>fifteen ways to hurt an opponent, and an <br>additional eight ways to hurt an opponent <br>real bad. He can take significant amounts of <br>damage and stay standing, leveling devastating <br>damage on her opponents. He typically is augmented with significant <br>amounts of cyberware and bioware to make him exceptionally tough <br>and dangerous in physical and armed combat. While he is ferocious <br>and deadly, he tends to have a code—it may be a code comprehensible <br>only to him, but it’s something. Body, Strength, and Agility are important <br>attributes for characters that are street samurai</div></div></div></div>
</div>
