<div class="inner" id="msg_686876">There are people who steal from the rich and give to the poor, and people who steal from the rich and laugh at the poor.<br>少译了劫富济贫的这一群人<br><br>Take your best shot, fight the odds, hope for the best, and show everyone you have the guts and the skills to do the impossible.<br>全力出击，挑战不可知的命运，祈祷你能成功，并且让所有人都看到你有让不可能变为可能的胆量和手段。<br><br>but you can take pride in the fact that you’ve earned everything you own—including your freedom.<br>猜想你把fact看成了face？<br><br>Common Character Concepts and their Roles Explained gives you a snapshot of the character types your most likely to find in the shadows.<br>常见角色概念与定位解释为你列出了阴影世界中最常见的人物类型。<br><br>blending their talents, skills, and specialized expertise to complete missions they would not be able to pull off as individuals.<br>联合各自的专长，技能，和专业领域来完成他们单枪匹马时难以完成的任务。<br><br>This gallery is just a starting point—there are characters in the shadows that don’t conform to any list.<br>这一节只是抛砖引玉，暗影世界中有的是没法划入任何一类的人物。<br><br>their SINless parents<br>SINless相当于没身份证的，具体参见俚语表<br><br>Depending on the tradition, <br>tradition在martian那里翻译成流派了<br><br>hacking into computers, commlinks, and datahavens.<br>猜想你把haven看成heaven了？<br><br>she has a whole bunch of options to keep herself involved in unfolding combat. <br>谍客有各种手段来确保自己在爆发的战斗中有所建树。<br><br>... in physical and armed combat.<br>在<del>现实世界的</del>武装冲突中。<br><br></div>
