<h5 id="subject_749003">
<a href="?PHPSESSID=d02c2b8ebfdf44378e526f6c0f474323&amp;topic=72895.msg749003#msg749003" rel="nofollow">Re: 【暗影狂奔第五版核心规则书翻译】创建人物 p.62 --  </a>
</h5>
<div class="zh_convert" style="float:right;display:none">
[<a href="javascript:convertToTraditional(document.getElementById('msg_749003'));undefined;">繁</a>
<a href="javascript:convertToSimplified (document.getElementById('msg_749003'));undefined;">简</a>]</div>
<div class="smalltext">&#171; <strong>回帖 #3 于:</strong> 2015-09-02, 周三 23:05:24 &#187;</div>
<div id="msg_749003_quick_mod"></div>
