<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_749003">以下内容和之前内容联系较大，所以就回复在这里，方便大家阅读。<br><br><strong>范例</strong><br><strong>开始</strong><br>　　James、Rob和Kyra正在为一场《暗影狂奔》的游戏创建新的人物。他们的游戏主持人是Michael。在和玩家讨论过他们想要进行怎样的游戏后，Michael决定起始等级是有经验的狂奔者（默认等级）。James决定扮演一个在街头长大的技术巫师。Rob想要创建街头武士，其背景是曾在加美联邦（UCAS）的军队服役。Kyra选择成为一名无码者和神秘修士，结合施展法术和附魔身体的能力。Kyra还决定加入一些社交技能来完善她的本领。<br>　　James、Rob和Kyra认为如下特质对于他们的人物来说是很重要的。在人物创建的后续过程中，他们可能会选择购买其他适合他们的人物属性和技能的特质。<br><br><strong>James</strong><br><strong>技术巫师</strong><br>自然挂载（花费：10业力）<br><br><strong>Rob</strong><br><strong>街头武士</strong><br>有码者【国家】（奖励：5业力）<br>优越属性【力量】（花费：14业力）【需游戏主持人批准】<br><br><strong>Kyra</strong><br><strong>神秘修士</strong><br>精魂导师（花费：5业力）<br>集中专注【等级2】（花费：8业力）<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">EXAMPLE<br>GETTING STARTED<br>&nbsp; James, Rob, and Kyra are putting together new characters for a Shadowrun game. Their gamemaster is Michael. After talking with the players about what they are looking for in a game, Michael has determined that the starting level will be experienced runner (the default level). James has decided he wishes to play a technomancer who grew up on the streets. Rob wants to put together a street samurai, whose background includes service in the military of the United Canadian American States (UCAS). Kyra has chosen to be a SINless mystic adept, combining the abilities of spellslinging with a body enhanced by magic abilities. Kyra has also decided to add some social skills to her repertoire. <br>&nbsp; James, Rob and Kyra have determined the following qualities are important to their characters. Later in the character creation process, they may select other qualities to purchase that will work well with the characters&#039;attributes and skills. <br><br>JAMES<br>Technomancer<br>Natural Hardening (Cost: 10 Karma)<br><br>ROB<br>Street Samurai<br>SINner [National]: (Bonus: 5 Karma)<br>Exceptional Attribute [Strength]: (Cost: 14 Karma) <br>[Dependent on gamemaster approval]<br><br>KYRA<br>Mystic Adept<br>Mentor Spirit (Cost: 5 Karma)<br>Focused Concentration [Rating 2] (Cost: 8 Karma)</div></div></div><br><strong>边栏——代替玩法</strong><br>　　除了正常的有经验的玩家以外，《暗影狂奔》为玩家提供了两种创建人物的代替方法。第一种是街头等级人物；这些人物还没有打响他们狂奔者的名气，他们依然还在为自己赢得街头信誉的过程中。显而易见，这些人物不会拥有和有经验的暗影狂奔者相同的装备和资源。第二种选项是精英狂奔者，创建的人物已成功地在暗影中狂奔了足够长的时间，使得他们成为约翰逊先生眼中的专业人士。他们拥有装备、人脉和才能来支持这些声誉。以下是代替玩法的规则：<br><br><strong>街头等级</strong><br>将优先级表的资源栏调整如下<br>优先级A：75000新円<br>优先级B：50000新円<br>优先级C：25000新円<br>优先级D：15000新円<br>优先级E：6000新円<br>业力：每位玩家获得13点业力来创建人物（最大26点业力）。<br>装备限制：设备等级必须为4或更低。最大可获得界限为10或更低。<br>新円限制：人物最多只能用5业力获取额外新円（10000新円）。<br>遵循本章人物创建和发展的其他所有规则。<br><br><strong>精英狂奔者</strong><br>将优先级表的资源栏调整如下<br>优先级A：500000新円<br>优先级B：325000新円<br>优先级C：210000新円<br>优先级D：150000新円<br>优先级E：100000新円<br>业力：每位玩家获得35点业力来创建人物（最大70点业力）。<br>装备限制：设备等级必须为6或更低。最大可获得界限为15或更低。<br>新円限制：人物最多只能用25业力获取额外新円（50000新円）。<br>业力限制：人脉的免费业力从魅力×3替换为魅力×6。<br>遵循本章人物创建和发展的其他所有规则。<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">ALTERNATE GAMEPLAY<br>Shadowrun provides players with two alternate ways of building characters besides the normal experienced players. The first is for street-level characters; characters that have not yet had a chance to establish themselves as runners and are still in the process of earning their street cred. Obviously, these characters will not have the same gear or resources as the experienced shadowrunner. The second option is the prime runner build to create a character who has successfully been running the shadows long enough to have established their reputations as professionals in the eyes of Mr. Johnson. They possess the gear, the connections, and the talent to back up those reputations. The following are the rules for each level of alternate game play:<br><br>STREET-LEVEL PLAY<br>Modify the resources column on the Priority Table as follows:<br>Priority A: 75,000 nuyen<br>Priority B: 50,000 nuyen<br>Priority C: 25,000 nuyen<br>Priority D: 15,000 nuyen<br>Priority E: 6,000 nuyen<br>Karma: Each player receives 13 Karma to customize characters (maximum of 26 Karma).<br>Gear Restrictions: Device Ratings must be rated at 4 or less. Maximum Availability is limited to 10 or less.<br>Nuyen Restrictions:&nbsp; Characters may only convert up to 5 Karma into nuyen (10,000 nuyen).<br>Follow all other rules for Character Creation/Advancement as laid out in this chapter.<br><br>PRIME RUNNER PLAY<br>Modify the resources column on the Priority Table as follows:<br>Priority A: 500,000 nuyen<br>Priority B: 325,000 nuyen<br>Priority C: 210,000 nuyen<br>Priority D: 150,000 nuyen<br>Priority E: 100,000 nuyen<br>Karma:&nbsp; Each player receives 35 Karma to customize characters (maximum of 70 Karma).<br>Gear Restrictions: Device Ratings must be rated at 6 or less. Maximum Availability is 15 or less. <br>Nuyen Restrictions: Characters may convert up to 25 Karma into nuyen (50,000 nuyen).<br>Karma Restrictions:&nbsp; Instead of the normal Charisma x 3 Karma for contacts, increase this amount to Charisma x 6 Karma for contacts.<br>Follow all other rules for Character Creation/Advancement as laid out in this chapter.</div></div></div></div>
</div>
</div>
